# Cloudflare Pages redirects
# Redirect www to non-www (preserve path and query parameters)
https://www.resumelink.cloud/* https://resumelink.cloud/:splat 301!
www.resumelink.cloud/* resumelink.cloud/:splat 301!

# Custom redirects
/about/ /about-wendy/ 301!
/rlog/ /blog/ 301!

# Force HTTPS
http://resumelink.cloud/* https://resumelink.cloud/:splat 301!
http://www.resumelink.cloud/* https://resumelink.cloud/:splat 301!

## Ensure dedicated 404 route responds with 404 (not overridden by SPA fallback)
/404 /404.html 404

## Serve directory pages without trailing slash as 200 (avoid 308 without headers)
/roadmap /roadmap/index.html 200
/terms /terms/index.html 200
/privacy /privacy/index.html 200

# SPA fallback for Astro static site
/*    /index.html   200
